## VNDS Interpreter for KT

This repository is a copy of KUAL application for Kindle from [mobileread thread](https://www.mobileread.com/forums/showthread.php?t=210496) by *qwertycz*.
Original post:

> Visual novels are type of japanese computer games (sort of). Its bunch of pictures, sounds and text presented in right order, and in right time u can alter story by making a choice. Since it isnt really comfortable to play these on your computer, some guy named Jake developed DS program and way to make these games more compact.
> 
> And this is it. I made VNDS interpreter for kindle touch, some of it is in javascript , audio in c.
> 
>  #### DISCLAIMER
> I developed and tested it on KT version 5.3.2 and later on 5.3.2.1 other versions can differ from what it should look like and work. Also i didnt bricked kindle in process, but it can happen since kindles bricking themselves even without any modifications.
> 
> #### DISCLAIMER
> Download VNDS 1.0, extract zip to your root directory.
> 
> #### GAMES
> 1. find your game, take android optimized version since i didnt tested DS ones
> 2. put everything in *extensions/VNDS/files/games/yourgamename/*
> 3. extract zip files in game directory to their coresponding directories:
>  *background.zip* => *background/*
>  *sound.zip* => *sound/*
>  *foreground.zip* => *foreground/*
>   *script.zip* => *script/*
> 4. continue with step 1 for another game
> 
> #### ???

> #### PROFIT
> Enjoy.
### Controls
* Top-left: Menu
* Bottom-left: Text-History
* Top-center: Hide Text
* Top-right: Refresh Screen
* Other area: Next
